preference.name: AIE_named_refs_to_export
preference.preference_description: Preference that allows a user to specify the named references to export to a connection. Valid values are all/select/primary. all - All the named references in the dataset will be exported. select - A dialog will be displayed that will provide an option to the user to select the named references. primary - Primary named reference for the dataset will be exported.
